Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.16,0:00:05.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最近好像有点热
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.82,0:00:06.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真听话
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.80,0:00:14.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别说夏天  连梅雨季节都还没到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.98,0:00:19.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的心永远都是火热的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.95,0:00:24.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又想到什么鬼主意了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.56,0:00:28.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谦吾
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.53,0:00:30.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你该悠着点
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.78,0:00:35.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绷紧的线会被轻易斩断
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.44,0:00:39.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但若是随着风而动的线  要斩断它就极其困难了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.19,0:00:41.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底想说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.84,0:00:42.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.48,0:00:46.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这里悠悠地帮忙想下该怎么玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.19,0:00:53.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打算做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.96,0:00:56.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,纳凉试胆大会
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.69,0:00:58.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还没到那季节吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.73,0:01:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很有趣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.62,0:01:01.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也要…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.54,0:01:02.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,参加
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.78,0:01:04.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要  会被杀掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.53,0:01:06.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没那么严重吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.52,0:01:07.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.67,0:01:11.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我所知道的离奇故事中  一般都被杀掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.53,0:01:15.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夜晚校舍的二楼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.78,0:01:19.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敲一敲女厕所从右边数起的第二道门
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.99,0:01:23.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要穿红衣吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.60,0:01:25.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要穿青衣吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.25,0:01:29.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要穿黄衣吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.26,0:01:31.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是回答红衣的话
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.85,0:01:34.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全身都会沾满鲜血
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.28,0:01:37.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是回答青衣的话
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.28,0:01:40.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,血被抽走  全身变得铁青
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.03,0:01:43.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黄  黄衣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.05,0:01:44.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黄衣？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.52,0:01:50.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被强迫吃下大量香蕉  全身变成黄色
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.52,0:01:55.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.70,0:03:29.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一届Little Busters
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.11,0:03:34.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,试胆恐怖纳凉大会
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.11,0:03:34.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs18\fsp0\pos(343,328))}NO·RYO
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.60,0:03:35.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请鼓掌
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.01,0:03:42.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请问什么是试胆大会
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.40,0:03:45.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小库  就是那个啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.13,0:03:49.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样握着锥子  在手指间…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.58,0:03:51.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当当当
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.29,0:03:53.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真要这么做吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.73,0:03:55.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要这么做吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.36,0:03:56.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  不需要
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.84,0:04:02.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到四张我放在校舍各层的纸条  然后回到这里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.08,0:04:04.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终点就在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.97,0:04:07.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好正式的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.45,0:04:09.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首先是分配队伍
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.66,0:04:17.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要和理树天各一方了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.54,0:04:22.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.19,0:04:23.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的  大姐头
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.12,0:04:24.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.14,0:04:26.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那首先出发的是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.62,0:04:27.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,铃所在的A队
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.99,0:04:30.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回  回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.56,0:04:33.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.80,0:04:35.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,…的说
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.05,0:04:41.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好黑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.72,0:04:44.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可怕  一点都不可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.56,0:04:50.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Call me for help！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.36,0:04:56.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有威尔卡和斯特莱尔卡在的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.60,0:04:59.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就没什么好怕了的说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.58,0:05:05.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么出发吧  工匠之神
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.67,0:05:10.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不肯跟来的说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.51,0:05:17.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大概是被风纪委员教训过不能进入校舍
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.39,0:05:18.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.16,0:05:22.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚安  威尔卡  斯特莱尔卡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.10,0:05:29.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办  好害怕的说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.19,0:05:31.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.87,0:05:35.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猫咪们
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.05,0:05:38.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟狗不同  它们不听管教的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.11,0:05:41.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.08,0:05:43.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.21,0:05:49.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小毬
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.35,0:05:52.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,OK  出发的说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.68,0:05:53.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不害怕吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.41,0:05:58.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  跟大家在一起我就不害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.40,0:06:03.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然我不害怕  小铃和小库也不害怕了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.38,0:06:04.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.34,0:06:05.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我害怕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.68,0:06:08.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我也害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.05,0:06:14.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没…没关系  有我在呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.87,0:06:17.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下一队  差不多该出发了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.98,0:06:18.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.10,0:06:21.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,理树  跟我们走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.57,0:06:24.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肩并肩  迈着小步一起走
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.71,0:06:28.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像被带走的外星人一样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.66,0:06:29.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么出发吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.65,0:06:31.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Let's go！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.32,0:06:34.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开始是这里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.30,0:06:37.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.91,0:06:39.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好害怕的说
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.79,0:06:42.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们留在这里  我过去看看
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.77,0:06:46.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道那笨蛋老哥会设下什么机关
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.33,0:06:53.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了  让我去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.94,0:06:58.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大概没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.25,0:07:00.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小毬同学好帅
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.13,0:07:03.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我上咯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.91,0:07:09.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看见什么了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.28,0:07:11.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.02,0:07:24.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小毬同学？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.19,0:07:25.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小毬死了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.63,0:07:32.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚刚的「咿呀」是「Fear」的冷笑话吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.69,0:07:35.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别死  活过来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.05,0:07:38.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有脉搏  别放弃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.06,0:07:42.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来有人中招了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.56,0:07:47.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一张纸条在恭介的教室
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.75,0:07:49.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你去哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.71,0:07:52.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恭介的教室啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.03,0:07:53.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.23,0:07:55.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走这边更快
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.63,0:07:59.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.78,0:08:01.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别碍事！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.50,0:08:06.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雕虫小技
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.73,0:08:14.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,脸蛋好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.33,0:08:16.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是脸蛋魔人搞的鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.38,0:08:17.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔人？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.21,0:08:18.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有太阳穴怪人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.66,0:08:20.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.69,0:08:23.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黄衣！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.14,0:08:30.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然还是这边更…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.38,0:08:36.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黄色！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.85,0:08:43.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是好玩
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.82,0:08:45.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们都不害怕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.62,0:08:48.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「我好害怕哦  理树君」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.98,0:08:50.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没这么叫觉得很遗憾吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.59,0:08:52.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  也不是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.08,0:08:54.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好  要进去了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.15,0:09:01.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇  这个被诅咒的旋律是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.15,0:09:04.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是老式磁带机
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.64,0:09:18.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇  这个锐利的目光是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.66,0:09:20.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是亮闪闪的一日元硬币
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.33,0:09:31.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.82,0:09:36.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,血？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.89,0:09:41.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是断手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.14,0:09:46.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说起来过去还有断手拉面的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.69,0:09:48.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是手套跟番茄酱
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.73,0:09:54.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好  把海蕴倒进去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.78,0:09:59.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让滑溜溜的手腕正好能碰到脖子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.78,0:10:03.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只剩下理科室了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.98,0:10:06.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是唯姐  够可靠的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.12,0:10:07.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.45,0:10:12.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少年  接下来就交给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.87,0:10:19.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就从幕后慢慢地欣赏你们害怕的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.60,0:10:22.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太残忍了  大姐头
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.14,0:10:30.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说  能不能走慢一点
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.36,0:10:32.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚刚还一点都不害怕的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.01,0:10:38.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在唯姐身后我自信连大总统都能打飞呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.08,0:10:43.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在还是有点害怕  理树君好像不怕这些东西呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.48,0:10:45.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  我也害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.79,0:10:48.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然很可怕吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.88,0:10:53.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.01,0:10:56.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总  总觉得突然一股寒意
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.41,0:11:01.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道说是因为风？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.31,0:11:06.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么嘛  吓了我一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.14,0:11:08.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.39,0:11:10.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然还是该先…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.87,0:11:11.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.97,0:11:13.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唯姐呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.74,0:11:29.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Let's search的说
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.25,0:11:30.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小心一点
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.75,0:11:34.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是铃她们？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.06,0:11:36.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,似乎就在附近呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.19,0:11:40.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小毬  小毬
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.49,0:11:43.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别死  给我活下来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.10,0:11:50.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是小毬Max
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.05,0:11:52.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干脆利索地晕倒了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.99,0:11:54.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冷不丁地干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.67,0:11:56.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎  怎么办呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.46,0:11:58.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.10,0:11:59.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.34,0:12:03.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我掀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.11,0:12:06.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大姐头
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.40,0:12:08.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  在做什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.45,0:12:09.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么关系
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.64,0:12:12.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都是女孩子  也不会少块肉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.19,0:12:14.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,问题不在这里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.18,0:12:16.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.47,0:12:20.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小毬
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.45,0:12:22.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,复活了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.05,0:12:24.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叫醒人的方式好色情
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.05,0:12:26.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还说你怎么忽然之间就不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.61,0:12:31.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得还是来吓唬你们会比较有趣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.61,0:12:39.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,收集到几张纸条了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.34,0:12:40.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三张了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.66,0:12:43.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大丰收呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.76,0:12:48.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,库特
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.60,0:12:51.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们两位
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.18,0:12:57.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就这样go straight
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.73,0:13:08.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.63,0:13:11.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,撞在我柔软的肌肉上了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.49,0:13:16.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们两个待在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.83,0:13:19.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,库公就交给你了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.42,0:13:22.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也注意到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.67,0:13:27.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊  从刚才开始就一直偷偷看着这里让人超不爽
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.06,0:13:38.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,库特  库特
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.59,0:13:41.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直枝同学
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.51,0:13:43.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.59,0:13:45.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.56,0:13:47.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本以为是纳凉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.56,0:13:47.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs18\fsp0\pos(363,328))}NO·RYO
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.11,0:13:51.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但实际是怨灵
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.11,0:13:51.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs18\fsp0\pos(363,328))}ON·RYO
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.72,0:13:54.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,似乎没人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.56,0:14:03.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.29,0:14:05.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打不开
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.50,0:14:07.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么  怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.66,0:14:16.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么情况
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.44,0:14:20.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  是理树吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.86,0:14:28.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怨灵？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.82,0:14:30.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不太清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.76,0:14:32.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真人他们
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.34,0:14:38.09,up,NTP,0,0,0,,您所拨打的用户不在服务区内或已关机…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.97,0:14:39.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拨不通
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.24,0:14:41.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直枝同学
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.71,0:14:43.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.23,0:14:46.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.34,0:14:52.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种东西  不是恭介的作风
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.41,0:14:59.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就知道有人会想着逃跑
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.00,0:15:02.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早就布置好机关了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.96,0:15:05.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样才是恭介嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.81,0:15:17.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别这么做了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.07,0:15:17.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.02,0:15:29.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能在肌肉上战胜我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.73,0:15:31.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怨灵？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.65,0:15:34.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,库特说她感觉到了些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.10,0:15:36.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.74,0:15:37.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.91,0:15:39.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,试胆大会先中止
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.61,0:15:42.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从现在开始  来击退怨灵吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.29,0:15:46.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怨灵？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.35,0:15:48.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又是让人意想不到的发展
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.35,0:15:50.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然让人难以置信  但却不能视而不见
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.01,0:15:52.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,理树  来帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.89,0:15:53.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.23,0:15:55.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也要去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.65,0:15:56.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,铃…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.60,0:16:00.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也去  和小铃在一起肯定没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.27,0:16:03.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能拜托你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.17,0:16:06.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.90,0:16:08.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我也来助你们一臂之力
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.25,0:16:10.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.02,0:16:12.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mission Start！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.57,0:16:16.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一楼没有发现目标  Over
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.60,0:16:17.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,了解  Over
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.23,0:16:22.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看招
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.54,0:16:27.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有反应
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.19,0:16:31.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在二楼  准备包夹
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.13,0:16:35.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真人！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.81,0:16:43.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.97,0:16:44.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.54,0:16:45.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟丢了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.08,0:16:47.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的能抓到那种家伙吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.27,0:16:49.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,棗同学
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.93,0:16:52.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我找来了一位强力的帮手
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.27,0:16:57.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么我也要来…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.93,0:16:58.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干得好！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.01,0:17:03.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,西园  我们该怎么捕捉怨灵
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.55,0:17:07.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多一事不如少一事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.28,0:17:08.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可已经在多事了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.33,0:17:10.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么弱点吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.40,0:17:12.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想想…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.47,0:17:17.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,灵类生物普遍不擅长应付强烈的能量
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.53,0:17:22.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比如嘈杂的场所  刺眼的光线
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.60,0:17:25.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事情越搞越大了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.87,0:17:27.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我反而觉得很兴奋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.72,0:17:29.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,理树你怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.14,0:17:32.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.78,0:17:39.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三楼  没有异常
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.70,0:17:41.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千万不要疏忽戒备
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.90,0:17:43.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猫咪受惊吓了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.54,0:17:46.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请多加小心  它就在附近
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.50,0:17:49.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,西园同学由我来保护的说
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.77,0:17:53.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.60,0:17:55.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在一楼楼道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.35,0:17:57.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来这边了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.87,0:18:00.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恶灵退散  恶灵退散
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.90,0:18:04.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,退散  退散  退散…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.78,0:18:12.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,铃君  小毬君
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.82,0:18:13.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,OK
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.31,0:18:15.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来了哦  小铃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.45,0:18:31.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幽灵先生  来这边
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.48,0:18:34.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小毬  不能叫它！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.14,0:18:36.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.89,0:18:41.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去你那边了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.30,0:18:43.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,理树
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.70,0:19:21.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸟先生？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.08,0:19:23.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好大
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.08,0:19:26.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,滑溜溜的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.35,0:19:29.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别加海蕴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.14,0:19:32.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恭介…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.50,0:19:34.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.45,0:19:42.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙是小P
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.53,0:19:45.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小P？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.73,0:19:47.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.17,0:19:50.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以前去北海道旅行回来的路上
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.30,0:19:52.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有一只小虎头海雕很亲近我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.05,0:19:56.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,于是我给它取名为小P
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.90,0:19:57.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,百般疼爱
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.44,0:20:02.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么说来  的确和它一起玩过
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.38,0:20:05.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它可一点都不亲近我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.43,0:20:12.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  虎头海雕没法在家里养
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.70,0:20:17.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只好忍痛将它送回了北海道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.63,0:20:21.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道它是来见恭介的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.17,0:20:24.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.85,0:20:30.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一路辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.31,0:20:33.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小P
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.39,0:20:52.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小P  记得再来玩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.78,0:20:57.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全是恭介氏的错吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.39,0:20:59.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  这算什么嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.36,0:21:02.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  幸好它不是怨灵
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.36,0:21:14.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mission Complete！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.36,0:21:17.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是个火热的夜晚
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.92,0:21:24.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们是最慢的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.79,0:21:27.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们去哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.53,0:21:28.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真亏你说得出口
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.00,0:21:31.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,校长室的陷阱费了我们好大工夫
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.14,0:21:34.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  就爱胡闹
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.33,0:21:38.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么脸色瞬间变青了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.97,0:21:42.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…没有在那种地方设置过陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.85,0:21:45.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那…这个是？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.93,0:21:54.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得  还是把它烧了比较好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.24,0:23:29.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,西园同学总是用深邃的目光注视着天空
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.22,0:23:33.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,理树你打算邀请西园加入Little Busters吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.32,0:23:35.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  让她成为我们的伙伴
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.11,0:23:37.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mission Start！
